1
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,080
Who could have thought

2
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,760
that on the stage,

3
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,400
the ever-glorious Boss Mei

4
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,840
would actually do such a thing?

5
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:27,960
Boss Mei is not the killer.

6
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,120
She's taking the blame for someone else.

7
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,280
But Boss Mei

8
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,440
has clearly confessed to the crime.

9
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:36,880
Besides,

10
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,480
we saw with our own eyes

11
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:39,720
that she hurt Uncle Qin.

12
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,600
Did you really see it with your own eyes?

13
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,600
What we saw

14
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,560
was only what she wanted us to see.

15
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,320
By the way,

16
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,720
is Uncle Qin's injury getting better?

17
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,600
The hospital said

18
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,440
Uncle Qin's wound isn't deep.

19
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,680
He just lost a bit too much blood.

20
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,840
By my calculations,

21
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,160
it's about time he woke up.

22
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,440
Then let's just

23
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,720
quietly

24
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,000
wait for him to come to us.

25
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,080
Inspector Huang,

26
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,160
Yanhong... she

27
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,000
didn't kill anyone.

28
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,000
I beg you,

29
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,720
please release her.

30
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:31,720
The people...

31
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,240
I killed them all.

32
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,000
Uncle Qin,

33
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,640
why did you kill them?

34
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,000
Because Yanhong

35
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,280
is my biological little sister.

36
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,920
Our original surname is Xue.

37
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,080
Her name is Xue Huizhen.

38
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,800
My name is Xue Qihua.

39
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:03,800
Back then,

40
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,360
because I was drafted into the army,

41
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,800
I was forced to leave home.

42
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,080
The year I left,

43
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,680
Huizhen was not even fifteen.

44
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,320
Ten years later,

45
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,280
I made the bumpy journey back to Jiangcheng

46
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,720
to look for my parents and little sister.

47
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:21,440
Who would have known,

48
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,600
my home was already in ruins,

49
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,000
empty and abandoned.

50
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,480
How much is this?

51
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:35,960
I don't want it anymore.

52
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,640
Thank you.

53
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,040
Miss,

54
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,120
wait.

55
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,440
Huizhen?

56
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:11,280
Is your name

57
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,840
Huizhen?

58
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,320
Who are you?

59
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,200
How do you know my name?

60
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,440
I'm your brother.

61
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,760
I'm Xue Qihua.

62
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,400
The gourd.

63
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,440
Your gourd.

64
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,160
It was on your eighth birthday

65
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:42,880
that I gave it to you.

66
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,480
Have you forgotten?

67
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,680
Brother!

68
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,000
Brother!

69
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,600
Brother!

70
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,760
I finally found you.

71
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:14,200
Where have you been?

72
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,480
After finding my little sister,

73
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,320
I learned that

74
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,200
our parents had already

75
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,320
passed away nine years ago.

76
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,520
My little sister was all alone,

77
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,760
and was eventually adopted

78
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,400
by the boss of Hongfu Opera House.

79
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,320
He even changed her name

80
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,200
to Mei Yanhong.

81
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,080
Then since

82
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,400
you are biological siblings,

83
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,840
why does Boss Mei

84
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,200
call you

85
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,320
Uncle Qin?

86
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,320
I was a deserter

87
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,320
who played dead to escape the battlefield.

88
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,640
If people knew my identity,

89
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,320
it would definitely implicate my little sister.

90
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,640
So,

91
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,760
I changed my surname.

92
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,400
Whether in public or private,

93
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,600
we never addressed each other as siblings.

94
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,520
On the battlefield,

95
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,000
I was a deserter.

96
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,400
To my parents,

97
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,600
I never fulfilled my filial duties.

98
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,520
So after finding my little sister,

99
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,400
I secretly swore

100
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,720
that in this life,

101
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,520
I must do everything in my power

102
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:18,520
to keep her safe.

103
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:20,520
I would never allow

104
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,000
her to be harmed in any way.

105
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,520
So,

106
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,640
when you found out Xiao Yuejiao

107
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,320
was going to hurt Mei Yanhong,

108
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,760
you decided to get rid of her.

109
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,440
She poisoned my little sister.

110
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,960
I absolutely couldn't let her live.

111
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,840
The only meaning of my life

112
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,200
is for my little sister.

113
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,160
I knew Wang Wei died

114
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,280
because of Xiao Yuejiao.

115
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,320
Aunt Wang hated her to the bone.

116
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:45,840
So,

117
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,440
I secretly

118
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,760
shared the news of Xiao Yuejiao's return

119
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,520
with her.

120
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,960
Who knew Aunt Wang's first stab

121
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,840
didn't kill Xiao Yuejiao.

122
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,520
That's why I dressed up as Lord Guan,

123
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:59,760
and used the Guan Dao I secretly sharpened during the day

124
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,280
to finish her off with another strike.

125
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:11,960
What about Brother Bao?

126
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,520
Why did you kill him?

127
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:14,520
That day,

128
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,760
I was working.

129
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,840
I heard an argument from the Buddhist hall.

130
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,440
So I hurried over to check.

131
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:21,760
As a result,

132
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,600
I saw Yanhong with her clothes disheveled.

133
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,960
She must have been bullied by that jerk.

134
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,080
So,

135
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,960
I dressed up as Lord Guan again,

136
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,880
and quietly followed him all the way.

137
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,720
I went up and stabbed that jerk.

138
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,880
He was so scared and cowardly,

139
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,320
squealing like a stuck pig.

140
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,080
Thinking about it now,

141
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,080
killing him with just one stab

142
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,400
was too easy on him.

143
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,840
What about Mrs. Bao?

144
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,520
She slandered Yanhong

145
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,320
and kept trying to kill her.

146
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,320
Darn it, she deserved to die even more.

147
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:06,880
I would absolutely never allow

148
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,640
around Yanhong

149
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:11,400
the existence of any dangerous factors.

150
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,640
So,

151
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:15,000
I put on Lord Guan's python robe again.

152
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,520
I watched her come out of the hospital

153
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,080
and followed her all the way to the alley.

154
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:21,720
I'll kill you!

155
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,440
I want revenge!

156
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,400
I'll kill you!

157
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,760
Give me back my man!

158
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,160
Mei Yanhong!

159
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,160
I want you to pay with your life!

160
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,520
I'll kill you!

161
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,600
Mei Yanhong!

162
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,520
I want you to pay with your life!

163
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,760
I want revenge!

164
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,400
Then I killed her.

165
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,720
But I didn't notice at all

166
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,280
that her blood got on the costume.

167
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,520
Mei Yanhong

168
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,320
wasn't trying to kill you, right?

169
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,760
The two of us depend on each other.

170
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,520
Blood is thicker than water.

171
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,960
How could she possibly kill me?

172
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,640
Because she put

173
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,840
Lord Guan's outfit

174
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,000
in her own room.

175
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,200
The keys to the room,

176
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,840
only she and I have them.

177
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,960
So ever since you left,

178
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,000
she guessed that I was the killer.

179
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,760
To stop me from atoning with my life,

180
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,840
she accidentally hurt me.

181
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,840
She wanted to take the blame for me.

182
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,400
To protect me,

183
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,640
she said she was the killer.

184
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:02,680
Brother!
